<title>Lawpna Pak a Tuoi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nuoi simlei kumsawt gam a ting puoi,
 Lungkhama naubang kahna maw Lalpa?
 Nunnawpna'n sang muolpi a liem,
 Lawpna pak a tuoi.

[V2]
 Aw ka galdawt thangvan sang khu,
 Angel lenna gam lopi achun;
 Tatsaten chawlhna galmuong ah,
 &quot;Khawvel beimai ta hen&quot; a tiu.

[V3]
 2. Aw ka ngai paktin lunna gamnuom,
 Chullo ding Lal nunnem vangkhuo sat thak,
 Ei kai - in, naubang ei puiin,
 Kaplai ei nemin.

[V4]
 3. Belam No gam Zion ka tun tieng,
 Guol lungtuok gibang khenna ngai puong ie
 Lungsiet khawpi namtin chitin,
 Nunnawp kimna ah.</lyrics>
</song>